dc_creator_sm: Snohomish County Geographic Information System (GIS), Dept. of Information Services
dc_description_s: Cities is a subset of tax parcels extracted from the Integrated Land Records data set.  City boundaries are trimmed along the Puget Sound coastline to facilitate cartographic display and geographic overlay analysis.  Cities that are multi-polygonal will have one record in the attribute table, as the data format for the coverage and shapefile is based on the regions data model. "Holes" within city limits are preserved, with no attribute record for the unincorporated area.  Cities is updated weekly to reflect the most current information.
dc_publisher_s: Snohomish County (WA) Geographic Information System (Snohomish GIS)
